01:28:04,409 --> 01:28:07,538
The world is very ugly.

1394
01:28:10,666 --> 01:28:12,751
E killed...

1395
01:28:20,717 --> 01:28:25,472
The most beautiful thing...

1396
01:28:25,848 --> 01:28:28,267
I've ever seen...

