1400
01:28:49,830 --> 01:28:52,124
I remember her laughter.

1401
01:28:56,086 --> 01:28:58,172
Because...

1402
01:28:58,755 --> 01:29:03,260
She would never part of his ugliness...

1403
01:29:04,928 --> 01:29:07,014
Took her from me.

1404
01:29:22,654 --> 01:29:24,865
