1413
01:30:04,655 --> 01:30:06,740
I'm tired.

1414
01:30:06,949 --> 01:30:09,034
I am very...

1415
01:30:09,117 --> 01:30:11,203
Tired.

1416
01:30:53,370 --> 01:30:55,455
Nicholi?

1417
01:30:55,956 --> 01:30:59,376
