1418
01:31:05,174 --> 01:31:07,259
Nicholi?

1419
01:31:13,348 --> 01:31:15,434
My goodness.

1420
01:31:17,561 --> 01:31:19,646
Gotcha.

1421
01:31:21,231 --> 01:31:23,317
You idiot.

1422
01:31:26,862 --> 01:31:29,406
Today we paint.

1423
01:31:32,242 --> 01:31:34,328
Not funny.

1424
01:31:40,167 --> 01:31:42,794
We went to the field that morning...

1425
01:31:42,920 --> 01:31:44,755
And it seemed another person.

1426
01:31:44,880 --> 01:31:46,965
His palette...

1427
01:31:47,174 --> 01:31:49,593
Should always be the same.

1428
01:31:50,719 --> 01:31:53,931
Your colors are like the keys of a piano.

1429
01:31:54,056 --> 01:31:57,518
Musicians need to be always
in the same place...

1430
01:31:57,601 --> 01:31:59,228
To express themselves.

1431
01:31:59,353 --> 01:32:01,897
The great painters do the same thing.

1432
01:32:01,980 --> 01:32:03,899
He showed me a lot.

1433
01:32:04,024 --> 01:32:06,193
He flooded me knowledge.

1434
01:32:06,360 --> 01:32:09,488
A life of secrets ran like a river.

1435
01:32:09,655 --> 01:32:11,615
The sun is like a woman...

1436
01:32:11,740 --> 01:32:14,493
When he kisses her warm lips...

1437
01:32:16,411 --> 01:32:19,248
It leaves a little color everywhere.

1438
01:32:19,331 --> 01:32:23,418
I began to see yellows,
ochres, oranges and reds...

1439
01:32:23,544 --> 01:32:24,545
...everywhere.

1440
01:32:24,628 --> 01:32:29,383
And the forest is hot but calm.
The opposite of war.

1441
01:32:29,633 --> 01:32:32,261
Not only about the color temperature...

1442
01:32:32,344 --> 01:32:35,764
But it is the opposite on the color.

1443
01:32:38,058 --> 01:32:41,061
The forest has yellow and purple.

1444
01:32:41,270 --> 01:32:44,064
The grass is green everywhere.

1445
01:32:44,273 --> 01:32:46,775
Where the light passes, is pink.

1446
01:32:46,859 --> 01:32:48,944
Got it?

1447
01:32:50,154 --> 01:32:52,614
It was amazing what he could do.

1448
01:32:52,698 --> 01:32:55,242
In a few seconds he turned
something simple...

1449
01:32:55,367 --> 01:32:57,452
On something alive.

1450
01:32:57,661 --> 01:32:59,746
Must fight...

1451
01:32:59,997 --> 01:33:03,792
Must make way to give life to things.

1452
01:33:04,001 --> 01:33:07,254
You must feel the joy.

1453
01:33:07,421 --> 01:33:11,258
He?? showed me how to
make the sky vibrate.

1454
01:33:12,426 --> 01:33:13,760
Bravo, John.

1455
01:33:13,886 --> 01:33:15,345
Bravo.

1456
01:33:15,429 --> 01:33:17,514
This is life.

1457
01:33:18,098 --> 01:33:19,850
I feel the shadows.

1458
01:33:19,975 --> 01:33:23,479
I feel the sun approaching.

1459
01:33:24,104 --> 01:33:26,773
The joy of it all.

1460
01:33:28,859 --> 01:33:30,944
Bravo, John.

1461
01:33:35,157 --> 01:33:36,950
I have to thank you...

1462
01:33:37,034 --> 01:33:39,369
The time he spent with me.

1463
01:33:40,454 --> 01:33:42,539
I is that I thank him.

1464
01:33:42,748 --> 01:33:45,876
No, you showed me something...

1465
01:33:46,376 --> 01:33:48,796
I thought I would not see.

1466
01:33:50,380 --> 01:33:52,257
Thanks, Nicholi.

1467
01:33:52,382 --> 01:33:54,468
Thank you.

1468
01:34:08,565 --> 01:34:10,067
Better...

1469
01:34:10,192 --> 01:34:12,236
Say goodbye to his girlfriend.

1470
01:34:12,319 --> 01:34:14,238
Do not you think?

1471
01:34:14,321 --> 01:34:16,824
She's not my girlfriend, Nicholi.

1472
01:34:16,949 --> 01:34:20,911
Leave a note,
a beautiful letter or something.

1473
01:34:21,453 --> 01:34:22,955
Great, great.

1474
01:34:23,080 --> 01:34:25,165
I'll wait here.

1475
01:34:55,821 --> 01:34:57,656
Dear Carla...

1476
01:34:57,781 --> 01:34:59,449
You were right...

1477
01:34:59,533 --> 01:35:01,618
I was lost.

1478
01:35:02,494 --> 01:35:06,456
But finding my way was
very sweet and rewarding.

1479
01:35:06,540 --> 01:35:09,209
His words always accompany me.

1480
01:35:10,169 --> 01:35:12,045
Find your dreams too.

1481
01:35:12,171 --> 01:35:13,755
With Love...

1482
01:35:13,839 --> 01:35:15,924
John.

1483
01:36:01,094 --> 01:36:03,055
've Put your bags upstairs.

1484
01:36:03,180 --> 01:36:05,265
Thank you.

1485
01:36:06,058 --> 01:36:08,143
Whither?

1486
01:36:10,437 --> 01:36:11,855
I do not know.

1487
01:36:11,939 --> 01:36:14,024
I have to solve.

1488
01:36:16,151 --> 01:36:18,237
Good luck.

1489
01:36:58,235 --> 01:37:00,904
I went to the park and drew for hours...

1490
01:37:00,988 --> 01:37:04,283
Rehearsing what to say to my parents.

1491
01:37:04,491 --> 01:37:08,829
Finally, I thought
would be better to face them...

1492
01:37:08,912 --> 01:37:12,040
And let fate take care of the rest.

1493
01:37:37,483 --> 01:37:38,400
Health.

1494
01:37:38,525 --> 01:37:40,611
'Dastrovia'.
- 'Dastrovia'.

1495
01:37:40,694 --> 01:37:42,529
I enjoyed myself.

1496
01:37:42,613 --> 01:37:44,823
Good,
I'm glad to hear that.

1497
01:37:44,907 --> 01:37:47,242
We were talking about you.

1498
01:37:47,743 --> 01:37:49,953
Your friend Nicholi is a good man.

1499
01:37:50,037 --> 01:37:51,205
It is.

1500
01:37:51,330 --> 01:37:55,209
He?? was telling me how
