1501
01:37:58,086 --> 01:38:00,672
Glad you're back.
- Thank you.

1502
01:38:04,468 --> 01:38:06,553
Heard you met a girl.

1503
01:38:07,054 --> 01:38:08,138
Yes - Is it true?

1504
01:38:08,222 --> 01:38:10,307
Yes...

1505
01:38:11,058 --> 01:38:13,018
Want a drink?
- Please.

1506
01:38:13,101 --> 01:38:14,186
Come on.
- Yes.

1507
01:38:14,269 --> 01:38:16,355
Come.

1508
01:38:16,480 --> 01:38:17,898
It's good to see you.

1509
01:38:18,023 --> 01:38:19,775
Honey?

1510
01:38:19,900 --> 01:38:21,276
Good...

1511
01:38:21,360 --> 01:38:23,487
Your teacher...

1512
01:38:23,946 --> 01:38:26,031
Came to see his father.

1513
01:38:28,742 --> 01:38:30,911
Learned something?

1514
01:38:31,745 --> 01:38:33,455
Yes, mother.

1515
01:38:33,539 --> 01:38:35,624
A lot.

1516
01:38:36,500 --> 01:38:38,127
Good.

1517
01:38:38,252 --> 01:38:40,337
It is very good.

1518
01:38:42,798 --> 01:38:47,010
I still do not know what
Nicholi said to fix things.

1519
01:38:47,094 --> 01:38:49,179
But no matter.

1520
01:38:49,304 --> 01:38:54,601
My father and I never
talked about what happened that summer.

1521
01:39:01,942 --> 01:39:04,027
Never went to college.

1522
01:39:04,403 --> 01:39:06,989
Chose to study in the museum.

1523
01:39:08,699 --> 01:39:10,784
Especially art.

1524
01:39:11,827 --> 01:39:14,913
But there are other things in life.

1525
01:39:21,837 --> 01:39:24,339
Not helping.
- I can not fix.

1526
01:39:24,465 --> 01:39:27,301
I'm terrible at this.
- A little.

1527
01:39:27,509 --> 01:39:30,471
I understand a bit,
but can not get it from here.

1528
01:39:30,596 --> 01:39:31,597
So.

