1536
01:39:54,328 --> 01:39:56,413
Okay.

1537
01:39:56,830 --> 01:39:58,457
Okay.

1538
01:39:58,540 --> 01:40:00,334
See his mother.

1539
01:40:00,417 --> 01:40:02,503
See how she looks.

1540
01:40:02,920 --> 01:40:04,338
Look at you.

1541
01:40:04,421 --> 01:40:06,507
You are beautiful.

1542
01:40:07,049 --> 01:40:09,134
Dear.

1543
01:40:25,025 --> 01:40:27,110
Nicholi?

1544
01:40:28,821 --> 01:40:30,906
Nicholi?

1545
01:40:54,221 --> 01:40:56,306
Nicholi?

1546
01:40:58,100 --> 01:41:00,561
's How I like to remember it.

1547
01:41:00,644 --> 01:41:03,564
Your brush dancing on the screen...

1548
01:41:03,647 --> 01:41:06,650
Like a ballerina dancing on stage.

1549
01:41:10,904 --> 01:41:15,075
I would say that Nicholi
