1551
01:41:20,372 --> 01:41:23,459
But I think it would be
very presumptuous of me...

1552
01:41:23,584 --> 01:41:25,294
.

1553
01:41:25,419 --> 01:41:27,880
And perhaps a lie.

1554
01:41:39,224 --> 01:41:41,518
Nicholi died that spring.

1555
01:41:45,981 --> 01:41:49,026
A part of me died with him.

1556
01:41:51,361 --> 01:41:54,364
