1562
01:42:29,191 --> 01:42:33,445
Other interests have led
me to the west coast...

1563
01:42:35,906 --> 01:42:37,991
But as he grew older...

1564
01:42:38,283 --> 01:42:41,829
More ideas Nicholi returned to guide me.

1565
01:42:42,204 --> 01:42:44,748
