1566
01:42:48,168 --> 01:42:50,754
Still see men as trees.

1567
01:42:54,967 --> 01:42:58,595
How naked people dancing on the hillside.

1568
01:43:01,306 --> 01:43:05,018
Clouds are everywhere
in where angels soar.

1569
01:43:07,521 --> 01:43:11,108
It took me years to realize
that Nicholi had died...

1570
01:43:11,191 --> 01:43:14,903
