living inside me.

1571
01:43:15,028 --> 01:43:18,657
Waiting patiently me to share my journey.

1572
01:43:19,950 --> 01:43:22,161
But most important for me...

1573
01:43:22,244 --> 01:43:25,622
Kept his promise long...

